or: #000000;\"><em>You can install an older version of Acrobat Reader. For instructions, see&nbsp;<a style=\"color: #000000;\" href=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/content/help/en/acrobat/kb/install-reader-x-windows.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Install an older version of Adobe Reader | Windows</a>.</em></span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\"step section\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"step_par step_parsys\">\r\n<div class=\"parbase section text\"><a name=\"step_par_text_0\"></a>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">When the Opening dialog box appears, click <strong>Save File</strong>.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"image parbase section\">\r\n<div class=\"to400\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"cq-dd-image\" style=\"width: 100%;\" title=\"Click Save File\" src=\"https://helpx.adobe.com/acrobat/kb/install-reader-dc-windows/_jcr_content/main-pars/procedure_0/proc_par/step_2/step_par/img_0.img.png/save_file_dialog.png\" alt=\"Click Save File\" /></span></div>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</li>\r\n<li>\r\n<div class=\"step section\">\r\n<div>\r\n<div class=\"step_par step_parsys\">\r\n<div class=\"parbase section text\"><a name=\"step_par_text_0\"></a>\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<div class=\"text\">\r\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Press <strong>Ctrl+J</strong> to open the download Library. When the download Library window appears, double-click the .exe file for Reader.</span></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"note parbase section\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">&nbsp;</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"image parbase section\">\r\n<div class=\"to400\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\"><img class=\"cq-dd-image\" style=\"width: 100%;\" title=\"Open the download Library\" src=\"https://help